        "title": "UserField",
        "description": "A user selection field in a report.\n\nSubmission values are of type `object`, on the following format:\n{\n    \"id\": string,\n    \"first_name\": string,\n    \"last_name\": string,\n    \"phone_number\": string | null,\n}"
